---
title: Hacking price - 최저가 알리미
layout: layouts/default.hbs
jsfile:
- search
---
<div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1 class="h3">Hack<b>i</b>ng price</h1>
            <sup>최저가 알리미</sup>
        </header>
        <hr>
        <main>
            <form action="" method="" class="form-horizontal">
                <h2 class="h4">상품 최저가 검색 <sup>from NAVER 쇼핑</sup></h2>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="maker">제조사</label>
                    <div class="col-sm-10">
                        <input type="text" id="maker" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="Apple" required ng-model="maker">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="product">제품명</label>
                    <div class="col-sm-10">
                        <input type="text" id="product" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="iPhone" required ng-model="model">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="version">버전</label>
                    <div class="col-sm-10">
                        <input type="text" id="version" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="7" ng-model="version">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="option">옵션</label>
                    <div class="col-sm-10">
                        <input type="text" id="option" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="128GB" ng-model="option">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="not">제외 키워드</label>
                    <div class="col-sm-10">
                        <input type="text" id="not" class="form-control input-lg" placeholder="accessory adaptor" ng-model="except">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group range" hidden>
                    <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="min-price">최저 가격 제한</label>
                    <div class="col-sm-10">
                        <input type="range" id="min-price" class="input-lg" min="1000" max="10000000" step="1000" value="1000">
                    </div>
                    <output for="min-price">&#8361; 1,000</output>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group range" hidden>
                    <label class="control-label col-sm-2" for="max-price">최대 가격 제한</label>
                    <div class="col-sm-10">
                        <input type="range" id="max-price" class="input-lg" min="1000" max="10000000" step="1000" value="10000000">
                    </div>
                    <output for="max-price">&#8361; 10,000,000</output>
                </div>

                <span class="text-center">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success btn-lg" ng-click="search()">검색</button>
                </span>
            </form>
            <section id="category-list" hidden>
                <h2 class="h4">카테고리 선택</h2>
                <ul class="list-group">
                    <li class="list-group-item"><label><input type="radio" name="category"> 스포츠/레저 &gt; 스케이트/보드/롤러 &gt; 킥보드</label></li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><label><input type="radio" name="category"> 패션의류 &gt; 여성의류 &gt; 코트</label></li>
                    <li class="list-group-item"><label><input type="radio" name="category"> 디지털/가전 &gt; PC액세서리 &gt; 기타PC액세서리</label></li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section id="search-result" ng-show="result">
                <h2 class="h4">가격 확인</h2>
                <p><mark>{[{maker}]} {[{model}]} {[{version}]} {[{option}]} </mark>상품 <mark>{[{filterCount}]}</mark>개의 가격은</p>
                <ul class="list-group price">
                    <li class="list-group-item row">
                        <b class="col-sm-2">최고</b>
                        <strong class="col-sm-10">&#8361; {[{highPrice.lprice}]}</strong>
                        <a href="{[{highPrice.link}]}" target="_blank" class="media">
                            <div class="media-left">
                                <img alt class="media-object" ng-src="{[{highPrice.image}]}">
                            </div>
                            <p class="media-body">[{[{highPrice.mallName}]}]{[{highPrice.title}]}</p>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="list-group-item row">
                        <b class="col-sm-2">최저</b>
                        <strong class="col-sm-10">&#8361; {[{lowPrice.lprice}]}</strong>
                        <a href="{[{lowPrice.link}]}" target="_blank" class="media">
                            <div class="media-left">
                                <img alt class="media-object" ng-src="{[{lowPrice.image}]}">
                            </div>
                            <p class="media-body">[{[{lowPrice.mallName}]}]{[{lowPrice.title}]}</p>
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <p>입니다.</p>
                <p>※ <small>해외직구 상품은 24시간 이내 환율에 따라 원화 가격으로 표시합니다.</small></p>
                <hr>
                <p><mark>{[{maker}]} {[{model}]} {[{version}]} {[{option}]}</mark> 상품의 <strong>최저 가격</strong>이 갱신될 때마다 텔레그램으로 구독하시겠습니까?</p>
                <div class="text-center">
                    <a href="tg://resolve?domain=hackingprice_bot" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg telegram-icon" ng-click="subscribe()">예. 구독하겠습니다.</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <hr>
        <footer>
            <p>i.jarang.u</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
<div id="loader" ng-show="loading">Loading...</div>